{"tid":393533,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"平均月入幾多錢先接受到自己搬出去住？","createTime":"2017-09-09T10:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T13:57:26.000Z","uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7aaa6282a0012662e5617e98c506529c1eb84d53","tid":393533,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"假如你依家癡屋企住，每個月俾10k家用乜都包曬 <br />\n搬出去住既話乜都要自己俾曬<br />\n資產增長速度會變慢<br />\n你平均月入去到幾多錢，先會考慮搬出去住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3783b87b26fb1f15cae804d7f5bf7e160569d09","tid":393533,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"假設你現時總資產係零 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aab4d8c3befb20a72927bdbaad36e6021798b5a","tid":393533,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"應該要30k"},{"pid":"4aef6d2ccb7e6f3c64d2c1cbac2d5b22b2a163cd","tid":393533,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"假設你現時總資產係零 <br />\n搬出去既生活水平要有所提高 <br />\n同時資產總值要有穩定增長(可以俾自己向上流動)"},{"pid":"2aa8bcf0710a4b8f60649f978d4a7a745497c416","tid":393533,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"租10K <br />\n水電煤 1.5K <br />\n寵物 2K <br />\n食飯 6K <br />\n上網電話費 0.5K <br />\n娛樂/零用 6K <br />\n<br />\n有無補充 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bba15806094c3fd1c731a07ac61675da3c6bbd","tid":393533,"uid":19858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"要睇下你仲有無打算買樓<br />\n呢樣野好影響個結果<br />\n如果打算以後都租,咁可能25K都得<br />\n但如果租屋只係暫時有容身之所<br />\n仍會計劃買樓<br />\n可能要40K以上先會考慮<br />\n畢竟又要租又要儲<br />\n不過最好都係住屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fa39ea767ba2cd8501a17e37821909f9c66558","tid":393533,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT