K <br />\n水電煤 1.5K <br />\n寵物 2K <br />\n食飯 6K <br />\n上網電話費 0.5K <br />\n娛樂/零用 6K <br />\n<br />\n有無補充 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你搬咗出去住仲俾唔俾家用先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d36974042ff735aa0298ffe401998d6301287b8","tid":393533,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"屋企氣氛差: 30k<br />\n如果唔太逼切既起碼4,50k 啦"},{"pid":"3286379bf0716c65018fc1e4c6d7a5ed058d425b","tid":393533,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>租10K <br />\n水電煤 1.5K <br />\n寵物 2K <br />\n食飯 6K <br />\n上網電話費 0.5K <br />\n娛樂/零用 6K <br />\n<br />\n有無補充 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你搬咗出去住仲俾唔俾家用先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要，不過俾少d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c170e11f427ad8bf83c7d61fa42b5278f26d7625","tid":393533,"uid":120712,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"除非結婚，如果唔係幾多錢都唔會搬出去住，因為要照顧父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：60k per month"},{"pid":"bf219e2552b6690e4f80533b2f844426911ca49e","tid":393533,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"除非結婚，否則唔搬。<br />\n坦白講，慳好多錢。"},{"pid":"e3a7a48331f7246c1e1587a9cb1a667d2c2a5aa1","tid":393533,"uid":19660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:59:34.000Z","msg":"講真我覺得搬出去唔關錢事，係睇本身屋企住緊個環境<br />\n<br />\n好多人唔夠錢洗都要搬出去，都係因為屋企關係"},{"pid":"f7e237c6b0260e3bf08b331913219cf4653aa043","tid":393533,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"冇50k都唔敢諗"},{"pid":"26456d13b3d4c58beed7217ee2bec9e903b231a1","tid":393533,"uid":84951,"lik